snippet.title: Namco Museum Megamix - Galaga Remix - Full Playthrough
snippet.description:
The next remix game on Namco Museum Megamix played and cleared. Galaga remix on this game is so much fun, I love shooting down enemies and other stuff to get me points. My favorite part of this game is the boss battle at the end. It's very easy and fun. So yeah, that's Galaga remix cleared on Namco Museum Megamix. Thanks for Watching.
